{
  "stem": "6009.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I can't help you.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I'm a prisoner like you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I say, do to me what I want.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So he did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He gave me a paper I shouldn't go to work the next day.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was enough not to go to work.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And now I have to come down to the hospital.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "When I came down to the hospital, there was about 100 like I.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And Mengele were there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And there was a Polish doctor, what he was the general doctor from the hospital.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He spoke German, too.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He was very close with that Mengele, I think.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But Mengele gave him the authority he should look over those 100 people, whoever is good still for the camp, and whoever is not good goes to the crematorium.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You understand?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they came my line, and so he said, this one there, this one there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When I came in line, the Polish doctor asked me, what's wrong with you?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Asked in German language.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I know he's a Polack, and I answered him in Polish.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So he asked me, are you Polish?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I say, of course I'm Polish!",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I was in the army during the war.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I was on the front.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I was a war prisoner.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I'm here already four years, I can't take it anymore.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I have enough, that life.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So he said to me, I'm going to take you to a hospital and I will operate you.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And you going to be OK.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And he put me on the other side with other few boys what supposed to go to the hospital.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And the rest they took on a truck and took them away, right away, to burn.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "How do you think it was that the doctor picked you to go to the hospital?",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
